  "description": "Terran shared a Twitter post with me where someone was suggesting a Fallout video game original character where the jingles on their jingle dress were made of shell casing, and apparently, this whole history I have of jingle dress cone coming from that, is not found online. Instead, the history is that it came about because of the 1914 Influenza Epidemic, and from tobacco can lids, not TB and shell casings.\n",
